---
title: Pepper Jam Bavette Steak plus a Kale & Sweet Potato Jumble
description: This pork filet, smothered in a lush pan sauce, is inspired by the flavors of classic Southern cooking. The key is red pepper jam, which gives the pork a tangy, sweet-savory flavor. Joining the party is a jumble of sautéed kale, roasted sweet potatoes, and onions. With a meal so plentiful and delicious, who can resist all this Southern charm?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/686dfb328d751c3919190e89-afc31182.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/686dfb328d751c3919190e89-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 630 kcal
  fat: 31 g
